    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在有趣的回合制战斗中开战！从敌人手里夺回强大的宝物。挑战故事模式中的高难任务和惊喜关卡。使用拥有特殊技能的不同单位。根据地形灵活调整战术。简单易上手，却充满乐趣！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266580/extras/17a846ac40bbb2405065794d1e777b9e.poster.avif?t=1771977671\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266580/extras/17a846ac40bbb2405065794d1e777b9e.webm?t=1771977671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266580/extras/17a846ac40bbb2405065794d1e777b9e.mp4?t=1771977671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266580/extras/f44c0950d293b9bcefc006bdc249f20a.webp?t=1771977671\" width=286 height=40 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >灵活运用多种作战单位，各有所长。有的机动迅捷，有的火力强劲。每场战斗尝试新战术搭配，保持游戏新鲜刺激。通过不断调整阵容组合，让每场对决都充满未知乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266580/extras/ebc59e072b3b7955e63ce25cf40d8cea.poster.avif?t=1771977671\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266580/extras/ebc59e072b3b7955e63ce25cf40d8cea.webm?t=1771977671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266580/extras/ebc59e072b3b7955e63ce25cf40d8cea.mp4?t=1771977671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266580/extras/6be80b3b66b9fd61237edbb76f6fa6fd.webp?t=1771977671\" width=286 height=40 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地形会改变你的部队的作战方式，森林、山、道路都有不同的效果，有些地方让你更强，有些地方则会削弱你。想要取胜必须根据地形灵活调整策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266580/extras/4fffe72caacbd2fbe46fd079557b6571.poster.avif?t=1771977671\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266580/extras/4fffe72caacbd2fbe46fd079557b6571.webm?t=1771977671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266580/extras/4fffe72caacbd2fbe46fd079557b6571.mp4?t=1771977671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266580/extras/30eae85e33305542a9a85d1036d355b5.webp?t=1771977671\" width=287 height=40 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索一个融合2D和3D艺术的多彩世界。趣味十足的角色设计和丰富的背景画面，让每个场景都充满看点。活泼的艺术风格让故事和动作栩栩如生。从城市到森林，每个地方都充满生机，让你尽情享受战斗与冒险的双重乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266580/extras/977dc9dd7a4a324bc97c3455da76ca80.poster.avif?t=1771977671\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266580/extras/977dc9dd7a4a324bc97c3455da76ca80.webm?t=1771977671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266580/extras/977dc9dd7a4a324bc97c3455da76ca80.mp4?t=1771977671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
